verbose_text: The expression and secretion of VEGF by these cells was significantly downregulated following transduction with LV.shGPR91 or pre-treatment with 10 muM U0126 (ERK1/2 inhibitor), 10 muM SP600125 (JNK inhibitor) or 50 muM NS-398 (COX-2 inhibitor), and these differences were statistically significant (P < 0.01; XREF_FIG).
